---
---

<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="about-inner">
    <h2>The ground is shifting</h2>

    <div class="about-illustration">
      <img src="/generated/about-illustration.png" alt="Robot crew working together on a ship" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="about-illustration-overlay"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="card-icon-wrapper">
          <svg class="card-svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
            <path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z" />
            <line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="card-number">01</div>
        <h3>The craft is evolving</h3>
        <p>
          We're moving from writing every line by hand to directing, orchestrating, and
          collaborating. Less typing, more thinking. Less editor, more engineering.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="card-icon-wrapper">
          <svg class="card-svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z" />
            <path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5" />
            <path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="card-number">02</div>
        <h3>No playbook exists</h3>
        <p>
          The tools showed up fast — Copilot, then Claude, then agents that run entire tasks
          autonomously — and we're all figuring it out in real time.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="card-icon-wrapper">
          <svg class="card-svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="card-number">03</div>
        <h3>Your skills matter more</h3>
        <p>
          Systems thinking, taste, judgement, knowing what to build and why — those matter
          <em>more</em> now, not less. This book shows you how to wield them.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="personal-note">
      <div class="note-border"></div>
      <p>
        This book started with a boring fintech project — a CRUD app with open banking APIs and heavy
        i18n. I kicked off the design with Lovable and saw agentic workflows in action for the first time.
        I wasn't blown away — I could see how it was done. Then the Claude Agent SDK came out, and I
        used Claude Code to port the entire SDK from Python to Go. It was like watching the best movie
        in years. The planning, the refactoring, the way it reasoned through Python decorators versus
        Go interfaces — beautiful. I used over a hundred prompts. Today, with the techniques in this
        book, I could do it with far fewer. Not because the model got smarter. Because I did.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .about-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .about-illustration {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 16/7;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .about-illustration img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    opacity: 0.85;
    transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
  }

  .about-illustration:hover img {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .about-illustration-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 40%, var(--color-bg) 100%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .about-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    position: relative;
  }

  .about-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(232, 150, 62, 0.12);
  }

  .card-icon-wrapper {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .card-svg {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    opacity: 0.7;
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
  }

  .about-card:hover .card-svg {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .card-number {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    opacity: 0.5;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .about-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .about-card p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-card em {
    color: var(--color-accent-deep);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .personal-note {
    margin-top: 3.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .note-border {
    width: 40px;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-accent), var(--color-pirate-teal));
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 1px;
  }

  .personal-note p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-style: italic;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .about-illustration {
      aspect-ratio: 16/9;
    }
  }
</style>
